0\n|match_KNR_MPN=1\u20131\n|match_KNR_ORF=1\u20130\n|match_KNR_PSD=0\u20131\n\n|name_MPN=[[MEAP Nisou|MEAP]]\n|match_MPN_AKK=0\u20132\n|match_MPN_AKT=1\u20132\n|match_MPN_AMK=2\u20130\n|match_MPN_AMP=3\u20132\n|match_MPN_ANG=3\u20130\n|match_MPN_AOL=1\u20131\n|match_MPN_APL=2\u20130\n|match_MPN_ELN=0\u20131\n|match_MPN_EGR=4\u20130\n|match_MPN_THA=4\u20131\n|match_MPN_THL=0\u20131\n|match_MPN_KNR=0\u20131\n|match_MPN_ORF=2\u20132\n|match_MPN_PSD=1\u20130\n\n|name_ORF=[[Orfeas Nicosia|Orfeas]]\n|match_ORF_AKK=0\u20131\n|match_ORF_AKT=0\u20132\n|match_ORF_AMK=1\u20131\n|match_ORF_AMP=4\u20131\n|match_ORF_ANG=2\u20131\n|match_ORF_AOL=5\u20130\n|match_ORF_APL=5\u20132\n|match_ORF_ELN=0\u20133\n|match_ORF_EGR=2\u20133\n|match_ORF_THA=2\u20131\n|match_ORF_THL=0\u20131\n|match_ORF_KNR=0\u20131\n|match_ORF_MPN=1\u20132\n|match_ORF_PSD=1\u20130\n\n|name_PSD=[[Poseidonas Giolou|Poseidonas]]\n|match_PSD_AKK=1\u20131\n|match_PSD_AKT=1\u20130\n|match_PSD_AMK=2\u20133\n|match_PSD_AMP=0\u20136\n|match_PSD_ANG=4\u20131\n|match_PSD_AOL=3\u20131\n|match_PSD_APL=1\u20131\n|match_PSD_ELN=1\u20131\n|match_PSD_EGR=7\u20132\n|match_PSD_THA=2\u20133\n|match_PSD_THL=0\u20131\n|match_PSD_KNR=0\u20135\n|match_PSD_MPN=1\u20134\n|match_PSD_ORF=1\u20131\n\n|update=complete|source=\n}}\n==See also==\n* [[Cypriot Fourth Division]]\n* [[1998\u201399 Cypriot First Division]]\n* [[1998\u201399 Cypriot Cup]]\n==Sources==\n*{{Cite web|url=http://www.rsssf.com/tablesc/cyp99.html#fourth |title=1998/99 Cypriot Fourth Division |date=2016-01-14 |accessdate=2016-01-14 |publisher=[[Rec.Sport.Soccer Statistics Foundation]] |ref=harv}}\n\n{{Cypriot Fourth Division}}\n{{1998\u201399 in Cypriot football}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:1998-99 Cypriot Fourth Division}}\n[[Category:Cypriot Fourth Division seasons]]\n[[Category:1998\u201399 in European fourth tier association football leagues|Cyprus]]\n[[Category:1998\u201399 in Cypriot football]]\n", "name_user": "Bellowhead678", "label": "safe", "comment": "Anorthosi-> added 